<section class="space-y-6 text-center">
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">生きた日本語を、みんなで学ぼう。</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    日本語学習者が日常で出会った表現を投稿し、互いに学び合うコミュニティです。
  </p>
  
  <!-- MVP準備中バッジ + 投稿一覧への導線 -->
  <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
    <span class="inline-block rounded-md bg-black px-6 py-3 text-white font-medium">
      MVP準備中
    </span>
    
    <!-- 投稿一覧への導線 -->
    <div>
      <%= link_to posts_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" do %>
        📝 投稿一覧を見る
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
        </svg>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- 将来的な機能紹介 -->
  <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.949-4.255A9.863 9.863 0 013 12c0-4.97 4.03-9 9-9s9 4.03 9 9z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">表現を投稿</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">日常で出会った「生きた日本語」を投稿して、みんなで学習リソースを作ろう</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">みんなで学習</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">他の学習者の投稿から新しい表現を学び、コメントで交流しよう</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">進捗を記録</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">学習の記録を残して、自分の成長を実感しよう</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
